        <text>
            as it traverses national boundaries
        </text>
    </line>
    <line>
        <text>
            through undersea cables
        </text>
        <fRed>0</fRed>
        <fGreen>0</fGreen>
        <fBlue>255</fBlue>
    </line>
    <line>
        <text>
            or the wireless ether.           
        </text>
    </line>
    <line>
        <text>
